📦 RASCAL - Bill of Materials (BOM)

Complete parts list with purchase links for building the autonomous delivery robot.

🎯 Core Components
1. Microcontroller
Item	Specifications	Quantity	Est. Price	Purchase Link
Arduino Mega 2560 R3	ATmega2560, 54 Digital I/O, 16 Analog inputs	1	$12-15	Amazon

Why Mega 2560?
More pins and memory compared to Uno, necessary for GPS parsing and multiple motor control.

